strings:
<voice_0x01001743><se_def>Prince Charmles: How could you let them get away,
you incompetent rogues!?
<voice_0x01001744><se_def>Prince Charmles: How could you be so remiss as to let a ragged rabble like them rout you!? You rotten rascals!
<voice_0x01001745><se_def>Prince Charmles: I should have known better than to entrust my Princess's retrieval to a troop of reluctant roughnecks!
<voice_0x01001746><se_low>King Clavius: Then why don't you go after them and bring the Princess back yourself?

<voice_0x01001747><se_def>Prince Charmles: B-But...er...
I, I can't do that all on my own.
I'll send the royal gua<endash>

<voice_0x01001748><se_low>King Clavius: Typical. You think that just because you're a prince you can solve everything with money
and power.
<voice_0x01001749><se_def>Prince Charmles: B-But I got that huge Argon heart during the initiation... All by myself!
